{"tid":377893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎巴絲 想買部相片打印機 求推介","createTime":"2017-08-28T05:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T05:31:11.000Z","uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd860376138d4ced92891026f9e3b7aae5185408","tid":377893,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"雖然話現今科技<br />\n好多工具可以儲相<br />\n好似google drive嗰啲<br />\n但我想買部機玩印相<br />\n將當時當刻最靚嘅事打印出嚟做留念<br />\n<br />\n拎嚟整貼紙 明信片 相 都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位有無咩打印機介紹？<br />\n最好可以隨身帶住 像素唔太差<br />\n<br />\n我見網上好多推介 canon cp910<br />\n雖然拎出街難啲但有無巴絲有用？<br />\n評價如何？<br />\n<br />\n隨身拎嘅又有咩好推介？"},{"pid":"932ab041d24e04fb908b1089e0ced97a95742923","tid":377893,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"414101135ee533592bab4346c871c5aeb3abc27e","tid":377893,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9bc9eb8574f8ec720864c7df8eb8e55163eb6ae8","tid":377893,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"025043def206b17bdc8de05e91d3d3236c8348f2","tid":377893,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"51020be0d37dc36bdaa5c4d59ca1e148c8c03fe0","tid":377893,"uid":35034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ce0ead218204d32bf8cb9c42db3b0a90514ceb","tid":377893,"uid":83446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"我都想買<br />\n見有個fd買左部可以即影即有<br />\n又可以連藍芽print相<br />\n好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}